<h2 class="bold font-l">Clockwerk</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Clockwerk is the leader of the Fiendish Five, immortal enemy of the Cooper Clan and the Final Boss of the first Sly Cooper game. </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
